{"tid":2014479,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港歷史知多啲:今日題目係「皇氣」究竟咩係皇氣？","createTime":"2020-05-13T05:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T03:09:14.000Z","uid":268540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd03be339bf4fb287f640cd049018397cdecf7f","tid":2014479,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"「皇氣」是警察約定俗成的叫法。<br />\n　昔日香港警察因平定六七暴動有功，獲英女皇伊利沙伯二世頒授「皇家香港警察隊」之名，是以警察又稱為「皇氣」；香港回歸祖國後，雖然警察刪去「皇家」兩字，但人們叫慣了口難以改變。<br />\n　有人認為，「皇氣」是因為主權回歸前，本港的警徽上有皇冠的意思；事實上，主權回歸前的每個紀律部隊，包括消防處、人民入境事務處、香港海關、懲教署、政府飛行服務隊等，部門徽章均有皇冠，但皇氣卻是獨指警察。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">睇到呢到，相信大家都知點解「擒賊先擒皇」啦</span>"},{"pid":"7c641d860d35068709bf683bb5d8b0500403be73","tid":2014479,"uid":5406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T15:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67daf9d4565625f4855d06358808da045ba995ee","tid":2014479,"uid":52980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:08:27.000Z","msg":"正式宣布從今日開始<br />\n大家可以將皇氣改做狗除<br />\n<br />\n例句：有狗除，手足小心。"},{"pid":"e3c874ac571bc8a665345c4abd8b9366bae2e982","tid":2014479,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67daf9d4565625f4855d06358808da045ba995ee","tid":2014479,"uid":52980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:08:27.000Z","msg":"正式宣布從今日開始<br />\n大家可以將皇氣改做狗除<br />\n<br />\n例句：有狗除，手足小心。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QirvZLZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQirvZLZ.jpg&h=ea4cc0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係狗咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}